<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.0>intro-&gt;[introprefix]、[introsuffix] 在 [place_name]、[place_adjective] 定居點和 [place_summary]，倖存者找到了脆弱的立足點。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.0>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.1>introprefix-&gt;炸彈落下，舊世界崩潰後</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.1>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.10>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;飢餓席捲了他們的定居點，迫使人們絕望地走出已知的邊界去尋找食物。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.10>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.11>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;輻射風暴席捲了大地，毒害了地球和心靈，考驗著他們的決心。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.11>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.12>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;變異的野獸和扭曲的恐怖潛伏在黑暗中，威脅著每一步。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.12>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.13>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;倖存者之間的恐懼和猜疑日益加深，內部衝突破壞了他們的團結。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.13>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.14>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;舊日戰爭的幽靈在廢墟城市中迴響，敵對派係為爭奪以[place_powerCenter]為中心的搖搖欲墜的權力而戰。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.14>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.15>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;由輻射和污穢產生的荒地疾病席捲了整個社區，奪走了年輕人和老年人的生命，而且看不到治癒的方法。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.15>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.16>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;不穩定的水源要嘛乾涸，要嘛中毒，迫使人們踏上危險的旅程，前往遙遠、未知的綠洲。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.16>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.17>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;天空燃燒著火山灰和火焰，遮蔽了陽光，大地寒冷刺骨。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.17>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.18>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;敵對戰幫發動了殘酷的攻擊，夷平了農場和村莊，驅散了家庭，瓦解了脆弱的聯盟。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.18>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.19>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;舊世界的技術搖搖欲墜和崩潰，使得倖存者不得不冒著巨大的風險從廢品中拼湊出武器和工具。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.19>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.2>introprefix-&gt;核火災後</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.2>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.20>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;一種潛伏的、非自然的威脅——被科學扭曲的變種人變得瘋狂——的低語在人們中傳播了恐懼和偏執。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.20>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.21>response-&gt;[responseprefix], [responsesuffix] 在 [place_community] 這樣的中心周圍，[place_adjective] 人民聚集在一起，其中包括維持脆弱和平的 [place_job] 人。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.21>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.22>responseprefix-&gt;有些人轉向了舊的方式</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.22>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.23>responseprefix-&gt;領袖崛起——軍閥</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.23>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.24>responseprefix-&gt;他們與鄰近團體建立了脆弱的聯盟</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.24>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.25>responseprefix-&gt;其他人則擁抱殘酷的生存主義</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.25>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.26>responseprefix-&gt;宗教崇拜和奇怪的新信仰蓬勃發展</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.26>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.27>responseprefix-&gt;熟練的拾荒者和工程師重新利用舊技術</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.27>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.28>responsesuffix-&gt;以部落儀式和祖先精神為指導。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.28>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.29>responsesuffix-&gt;選舉產生的議會－每個議會都聲稱對自己的人民擁有權威。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.29>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.3>introprefix-&gt;第一次世界大戰留下的傷痕比沙漠和廢墟更深</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.3>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.30>responsesuffix-&gt;交易知識、武器和希望。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.30>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.31>responsesuffix-&gt;先發制人，對敵人毫不留情。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.31>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.32>responsesuffix-&gt;在混亂中提供意義。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.32>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.33>responsesuffix-&gt;保衛和維持他們的家園。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.33>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.34>transformation-&gt;[transformationprefix], [transformationsuffix] 他們的大廳，就像[place_powerCenter]一樣，成為混亂中秩序的象徵。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.34>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.35>transformationprefix-&gt;隨著時間的推移，他們的習俗變成了法律</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.35>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.36>transformationprefix-&gt;最初是分散的倖存者成長為一股強大的力量</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.36>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.37>transformationprefix-&gt;他們的旗幟在戰場和議會大廳中升起</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.37>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.38>transformationprefix-&gt;有的定居在古城廢墟上</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.38>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.39>transformationprefix-&gt;苦難的傷痕烙印在他們身上</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.39>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.4>introprefix-&gt;當文明墮落時</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.4>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.40>transformationprefix-&gt;傳奇圍繞著他們的領導者而成長</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.40>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.41>transformationsuffix-&gt;儀式和牢不可破的誓言。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.41>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.42>transformationsuffix-&gt;整個荒原都令人畏懼和尊敬。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.42>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.43>transformationsuffix-&gt;團結和力量的象徵。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.43>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.44>transformationsuffix-&gt;將衰敗變成希望的堡壘。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.44>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.45>transformationsuffix-&gt;造就了一支永遠不會向牆外的恐怖低頭的民族。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.45>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.46>transformationsuffix-&gt;火光講述的故事激勵著後代。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.46>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.47>legacy-&gt;[legacyprefix], [legacysuffix] 曾經只是 [place_name] 的一群倖存者，現在他們成為了堅韌的證明。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.47>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.48>legacyprefix-&gt;現在</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.48>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.49>legacyprefix-&gt;從破碎的開始</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.49>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.5>introsuffix-&gt;分散的倖存者在受輻射的廢墟中勉強度日。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.5>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.50>legacyprefix-&gt;他們的故事是關於韌性的故事</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.50>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.51>legacyprefix-&gt;雖然廢棄物很嚴重</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.51>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.52>legacyprefix-&gt;當舊世界逐漸消失</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.52>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.53>legacyprefix-&gt;時間會審判他們</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.53>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.54>legacysuffix-&gt;他們的名字在荒原上迴響，是盟友的燈塔，也是敵人的警告。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.54>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.55>legacysuffix-&gt;他們在新世界中佔有一席之地，從灰燼中塑造未來。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.55>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.56>legacysuffix-&gt;證明了在廢墟中團結的力量。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.56>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.57>legacysuffix-&gt;他們的遺產永垂不朽——銘刻在石頭上，在風中低語。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.57>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.58>legacysuffix-&gt;他們的新秩序崛起，這是這片蠻荒土地上脆弱的希望。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.58>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.59>legacysuffix-&gt;他們是救世主還是怪物——但他們的影響是不可否認的。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.59>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.6>introsuffix-&gt;灰燼中誕生了新的部落、幫派和為生存而奮鬥的定居點。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.6>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.7>introsuffix-&gt;從這些傷痕中誕生了羽翼未豐的社區。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.7>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.8>introsuffix-&gt;絕望的人們和充滿希望的人聚集在破碎的天空下閃爍的營火周圍。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.8>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.9>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;他們與[place_foeLeader]所領導的野蠻攻擊者作戰，指揮著冷酷無情的[place_foeSoldiers]。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.9>
</LanguageData>
